description:

Luciferian eye: In occult circles this symbolizes Lucifer.

the chrome logo:

The first Apple computer was sold at $666.66 because Wozniak “liked repeating digits”. You’ll find that a majority of corporate logos find their design in esoteric and occult symbols from antiquity. The eye of providence or “all seeing eye” is found everywhere, some are more bold as to include the sigil of Lucifer in their logo. Also plenty of pentagrams and inverted pentagrams.
